channel.title: How do i add a wilderness skull when you enter wild on ayudascape V.3 source?
channel.description:
Hello, Ive been trying to add this for hours then finally gave up and came here! Please, if you have ever downloaded ayudascape V.2 or another source which has the wilderness skull on the downright corner of the screen that has a skull and says something like "wild" or "safe". Remember, i want the answer! So don't tell me gay information! I want useful information so yea.... If i can't do it, i will politely ask you to do it for me if your nice enough! If you are, then i'll put you in credits XD! This is my #1 lol top priority atm so please reply because I do not know where the skull code is on Ayudascape V.3, xx nub xx has it all messed up (compared to his V.2) :( i REALLY need help or i will not come out with another server for a while!!!!!
Thank you, -Zaron
